    todo: "Drink 2-4 cups of filtered coffee in the morning hours. Avoid coffee after ~2 PM if you're not a known fast metabolizer (caffeine half-life ~5h, longer in slow metabolizers). Don't add 4 sugars and cream — that wipes out the metabolic benefit. Black, with milk, or with a small amount of sugar is fine. Decaf still has chlorogenic acid but loses the caffeine-related benefits.",
