    one: "Cheap amino acid with small but consistent RCT evidence for improving sleep onset and quality.",
    plain: "A cheap amino acid (a building block of protein, like in collagen) that helps you fall asleep faster. Small studies show 3g before bed cuts sleep onset time and improves sleep quality. Effect is modest but real and consistent across studies.",
